{"tid":1198104,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[反送中]星期三揸車堵塞中環及過海隧道!","createTime":"2019-06-10T06:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T10:48:45.000Z","uid":157081,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"54f4aec60afe9c1f773ad8b0da2aef2885ce25a7","tid":1198104,"uid":157081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:45:21.000Z","msg":"有冇人一齊揸車堵塞中環附近主要幹道？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個方法比起昨晚大家衝擊立法會有成效得多,<br />\n相信幾百架車足以令港島甚至九龍交通癱瘓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地赤手空拳同班速龍根本無得玩,但如果我地揸車去堵塞道路,差佬根本吹你唔脹,最多咪拖你車,但幾百架,幾千架佢點拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拖車都過唔到嚟啦最重要大家人身都安全啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6a584776fc7a38e9cb1f44f98ee3031c234814","tid":1198104,"uid":157081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:48:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea5e8fa1be4596707ebabf542938f17d4d8c8d1","tid":1198104,"uid":157081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:00:22.000Z","msg":"大家一齊討論啦<br />\n俾更多人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099d2d37ea76224ddfb49e835a31107c5eaeace6","tid":1198104,"uid":19630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"唔好阻住人去立法會"},{"pid":"866ea4997a51b0225e31ca344c246d873144f42b","tid":1198104,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:32:39.000Z","msg":"惡意堵塞犯法架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2659d204da592ececb34ac510a69c5ead5cd400","tid":1198104,"uid":157081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"866ea4997a51b0225e31ca344c246d873144f42b","tid":1198104,"uid":196924,"li